# --- Lovable's auto-injected Supabase project (the local one Lovable scaffolded) ---
# These are committed by Lovable already; they're public anon keys, safe in source.
SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY="<lovable injects>"
SUPABASE_URL="<lovable injects>"
VITE_SUPABASE_PROJECT_ID="<lovable injects>"
VITE_SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY="<lovable injects>"
VITE_SUPABASE_URL="<lovable injects>"

# --- HealthyGram external Supabase (where the agent writes scored reels) ---
# This is the project the reels feed actually queries via the server function
# at src/lib/reels.functions.ts. The KEY here is server-only — never bundled
# into the client.
#
# Local dev: paste your Supabase service role key here.
# Lovable preview / production: set this in Lovable's Environment Variables UI
# (Project Settings → Environment Variables). Do NOT commit it.
EXTERNAL_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY="sb_secret_..."
